x(n)
x_{n+1}= x_n-x_n^2
x_0=a
0 \le a \le 1
\lim_{n \to \infty} x_n
x_n-x_{n+1} = x_n-x_n+x_n^2>0
A=\lim x_n= \lim x_{n+1}= \lim (x_n-x_n^2) = A-A^2 => A^2=0 => A=0
\lim_{n \to \infty} x_0^2+x_1^2+...+x_n^2
x_n^2=x_n-x_{n+1}
x_0^2+x_1^2+\ldots+x_n^2=(x_0-x_1)+(x_1-x_2)+\ldots+(x_n-x_{n+1})=x_0-x_{n+1}
x_0=a
x_{n+1}
n
